<p>Later that morning Edzer presented a poster on “openEO: an open API for cloud-based big Earth Observation processing platforms” (<a href="https://meetingorganizer.copernicus.org/EGU2018/EGU2018-8198.pdf">abstract</a>) in the session <a href="https://meetingorganizer.copernicus.org/EGU2018/session/28035">“Data cubes of Big Earth Data - a new paradigm for accessing and processing Earth Science Data”</a>.</p>

